0 HAVENHISTORY~
{128}
                                   History
{308}
Long time ago dragons were the ruling race in te Realms, they were the
ones defending the Lords. This until the greatest war between the elements
almost led to the extition of the dragon race. The examplars who managed to
survive retired from the battle. Evil dragons established their domain into
a tower that is well known by the majority of living beings, while lawful
dragons decided to hide themself in a secret place to restore their power
and to get ready for the next war. In the meanwhile the Lords, who lost their
army of dragons, started recruiting among the lesser races almost forgetting
about dragons. Realizing that there was no need anymore to get ready for a
war, lawful dragons transformed their secret refuge into a shining town. The
location of the the town was unknown for everyone, until Neptune managed to
locate its whereabouts, taking advantage of a period of weakness accused by
his ancestral enemies. The haven is now seriously threatened by a mighty
warrior, who received great powers by his master, sent there to destroy the
whole breed of lawful dragons.

