  tell $n Thanks to you our town will live for many centuries. I will never
  tell $n thank you enough. All I can do is to give my soul to you.
  tell $n Do you know how to CAGE the soul of a dragon?
  break
endif
if quest (3,1,$n) == 1
  tell $n Welcome in my Castle $n.
  tell $n I have been informed that you are seeking the soul of a Dragon.
else
  shout How did you dare, $n, to appear before me without permission?
  shout You'll be banned till you prove that you are worthy to stay here!
  mptransfer $n 9755
endif
~
